  "content": "\n \n \n  <h3 data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <section data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n      <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n       <section style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;text-align: center;visibility: visible;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n        <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0e64467b-f3af-49b6-08c4-6155152ec400/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.425\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;height:auto;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;vertical-align:bottom;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:1;\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"248\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"246\" data-imgfileid=\"505094178\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0e64467b-f3af-49b6-08c4-6155152ec400/public\">\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section></h3>\n  <h3 style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <section data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n      <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n       <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin: -1.2em 8px 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n        <p style=\"margin: -1.2em 8px 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-family: inherit;font-size: 1em;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">新智元报道 &nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section></h3>\n  <section style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：定慧</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n     <h5 style=\"padding:10px;margin:10px 8px 0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;max-width:100%;word-break:break-all !important;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">【新智元导读】</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">AI频频刷新基准测试纪录，却算不清「strawberry」里到底有几个字母r，在人类看来很简单的问题却频频出错。这种反差促使创意测评兴起，例如由一名高中生开发的MC-Bench，用Minecraft方块「竞技场」模式评价AI能力。这种新的测评范式，或许更贴合人类对AI直观、创造性能力的实际期待。</span><strong style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\"></strong></span></h5>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">「strawberry中有多少个r」和「在LSAT法学考试中获得88分」哪个更难？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">对于现如今的LMMs来说，通过各种人类「听着就头痛，看又看不懂」的基准测试似乎已是家常便饭。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">比如DeepSeek-R1发布时在6大基准测试（包含AIME、MMLU、MATH-500等）中超过o1取得领先。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/18361bac-eba3-4761-5761-805929009500/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7305555555555555\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"422\" data-imgfileid=\"505094191\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/18361bac-eba3-4761-5761-805929009500/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">但是对于人类来说依靠直觉和下意识就能回答的问题，LLM们似乎集体有点「发懵」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">很难理解OpenAI的GPT-4能够在LSAT考试中获得第88百分位的成绩，但却无法数清楚「</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">strawberry</span></span><span leaf=\"\">」中有多少r。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">除了复杂的基准测试，另外一种评价模型好坏的方式就是「竞技场模式」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">比如可以在Chatbot Arena进行上提问投票，选出面对相同问题时的「最佳模型」。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"294\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"505094192\" data-ratio=\"0.5092592592592593\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/17a0b15d-cfe6-4873-d368-b08069ffa400/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/17a0b15d-cfe6-4873-d368-b08069ffa400/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">但是这种依靠Chat模式的评测依然不太直观，于是各种各样的创意评测就诞生了。</span></span></p>\n  <section autoid=\"1895\" data-style-type=\"0\" style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-bottom:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section style=\"padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">创意评测的魅力</span></p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e54f28f5-a947-43c0-7a5e-0e4992567a00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.60625\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"341\" data-imgfileid=\"505094185\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e54f28f5-a947-43c0-7a5e-0e4992567a00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Minecraft Benchmark（或 MC-Bench）像一个竞技场，在一对一的挑战中针对相同提示生成Minecraft作品。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">「对决双方」由用户投票选择哪个模型做得更好。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">并且只有在投票后才能看到每个Minecraft建筑是由哪个AI制作的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">目前MC-Bench的榜单上，Claude3.7暂时领先，deepseek-r1位列第5，但是考虑到DeepSeek-R1的发布时间，Claude3.7、GPT-4.5和Gemini2.0都相当于是「新一代」的模型了，期待DeepSeek-R2出来后的榜单！</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/cc0eac79-37b9-44d1-34d4-0b78f1f6d800/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6231481481481481\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"360\" data-imgfileid=\"505094193\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/cc0eac79-37b9-44d1-34d4-0b78f1f6d800/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">像MC-Bench这样的创意评测，优势非常明显：普通人也能轻松参与，像「选美」一样简单直接。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">创造MC-Bench项目的仅仅是一名高中生Adi Singh，在将Minecraft用于AI评测这件事情上，Adi Singh觉得Minecraft的价值不在游戏本身。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">而是作为有史以来最畅销的电子游戏，即使对于没玩过Minecraft游戏的人来说，仍然可以选择自己更喜欢的「方块样子」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">MC-Bench是合作开发的，除了Adi Singh外，贡献者还有7位，包括了「提示词创意官」、技术主管和开发者们。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fb5e572c-7bcf-4f86-35c0-5c7929942900/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.975\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"564\" data-imgfileid=\"505094194\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fb5e572c-7bcf-4f86-35c0-5c7929942900/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">并获得了Anthropic、Google和阿里巴巴等公司的技术支持。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/95e86597-4e63-4507-8b78-b2c98a022600/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.37592592592592594\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"217\" data-imgfileid=\"505094195\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/95e86597-4e63-4507-8b78-b2c98a022600/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section autoid=\"1895\" data-style-type=\"0\" style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-bottom:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section style=\"padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">传统LLM评测：严肃认真但未必管用</span></p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">传统的AI基准测试技术被证明不足，主要体现在以下几个方面：</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n    <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">主场优势 (Overfitting to benchmarks)</span></span></strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">：传统的 AI 基准测试往往基于特定类型的任务设计，这些任务对 AI 模型来说相对固定且简单，这种过拟合就像一名「只会背题」的学生。</span></span></span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n    <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">测试任务过于狭窄</span></span></strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">：传统的测试任务多集中于单一维度的能力评估，如语言理解、逻辑推理、数学计算。</span></span></span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n    <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">缺乏真实环境与开放性</span></span></strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">：传统的基准测试通常使用高度抽象化或理论化的环境，而这些环境往往不能反映现实世界中问题的开放性和不确定性。</span></span></span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n    <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">难以衡量通用性与泛化能力</span></span></strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">：传统 AI 基准测试往往无法有效衡量模型的通用性或泛化能力。</span></span></span></p></li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">因此AI构建者正在转向更有创意的方法来评估Gen-AI模型的能力。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI开发者们表示，我们也想玩点「新鲜的」。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/966f4e11-be4d-4a74-83da-81cd71024300/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.46111111111111114\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"267\" data-imgfileid=\"505094196\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/966f4e11-be4d-4a74-83da-81cd71024300/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">MC-Bench的本质是在测试AI模型的文本理解和编码能力。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">通过类似Chatbot Arena的方式来进行模型评比。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2a1eb5d4-cc04-4f08-b155-08292a988000/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7453703703703703\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"431\" data-imgfileid=\"505094197\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2a1eb5d4-cc04-4f08-b155-08292a988000/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">对于为何选择游戏，选择Minecraft，Adi Singh觉得「游戏可能只是一种测试能动性推理的媒介，比现实生活更安全，也更适合测试目的，因此在我看来更为理想」。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">从Adi Singh个人网站来看，他对于使用Minecraft方块进行AI评测应该是「蓄谋已久」，Adi Singh展示很多利用大模型生成Minecraft方块的精彩案例。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">比如，</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;text-decoration: none solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);\"><span leaf=\"\">gpt-4.5根据提示「构建一艘在云层中飞行的蒸汽朋克风格飞艇</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">」。</span></span></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/42e65164-da9c-46e8-712b-bc742e031c00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9425925925925925\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"545\" data-imgfileid=\"505094231\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/42e65164-da9c-46e8-712b-bc742e031c00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;text-decoration: none solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);\"><span leaf=\"\">再比如，claude-3.7-sonnet有一个令人印象非常深刻的Minecraft模型，根据提示「</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">韩国友谊之钟</span></span><span leaf=\"\">」生成。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f01533ce-f31c-4269-939b-7a98aa7f0900/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7898148148148149\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"505094233\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f01533ce-f31c-4269-939b-7a98aa7f0900/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">并且，社区成员对MC-Bench的评价也很高。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8f54d21a-5766-440a-248c-d236b1c12000/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5398148148148149\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"505094234\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8f54d21a-5766-440a-248c-d236b1c12000/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">比如目前就职于OpenAI的基础研究员Aidan McLaughlin，对Minecraft Bench给予了很高的评价：</span></span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">你应该密切关注MC-Bench！</span></span></strong>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;text-decoration: none solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);\"><span leaf=\"\">Aid</span></span><span style=\"text-decoration: none solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">an McLaughlin同时给出了他认为最佳的人工智能基准应具有：&nbsp;</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">审计数据的乐趣 （与其他所有基准测试都不同）&nbsp;</span></span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">测试真正关心的功能 （代码、美学、意识）&nbsp;</span></span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">甚至可以辨别顶级型号之间的性能差异</span></span></p></li>\n  </ul>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1924b606-e499-4b49-0b24-2ecd9ac02c00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.45185185185185184\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"254\" data-imgfileid=\"505094232\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1924b606-e499-4b49-0b24-2ecd9ac02c00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section autoid=\"1895\" data-style-type=\"0\" style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-bottom:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section style=\"padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">游戏测评AI似乎依然是「主流创意」</span></p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">在Claude 3.7 Sonnet发布时说过，模型降低了在数学、竞赛和编程方面的特化程度，有「更好」的思考能力。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">那么如何评测新模型的「思考」能力呢？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">答案就是游戏《宝可梦》，这不是开玩笑。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Claude通过配备了透过程序来操控游戏的特定「按钮」。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">甚至还在Twitch上直播了Claude玩游戏的全过程，可以看到它如何学习、思考并采取行动。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0499419b-e68e-446c-b535-ff7f7faaf700/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5601851851851852\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"324\" data-imgfileid=\"505094198\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0499419b-e68e-446c-b535-ff7f7faaf700/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">不论是传统的基准测试，还是类似MC-Bench的创意测试。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">对于生成式AI的能力评测，目前依然没有一个「一劳永逸」的标准。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">传统基准测试的评估结果多采用单一的客观分数（如准确率），忽视了人类实际感受和主观评价的维度。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在生成式AI中，美学感知、创造力、直观性往往更加重要，但这些因素很难在传统的标准化测试中体现出来。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">也许类似MC-Bench这样的创意评测会给未来的AI评测带来新的「范式」。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">而新的AI评测「范式」也许会加速推动AI的发展。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">参考资料：</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-align:left;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">https://mcbench.ai/</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-align:left;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">https://techcrunch.com/2025/03/20/a-high-schooler-built-a-website-that-lets-you-challenge-ai-models-to-a-minecraft-build-off/</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-align:left;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">https://finance.yahoo.com/news/high-schooler-built-website-lets-201110310.html</span></span></section>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "高中生开发的 MC-Bench 利用 Minecraft 游戏，以用户投票方式对 AI 模型进行创造性和直观能力的评测，旨在弥补传统基准测试的不足，目前 Claude 暂时领先。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "高中生开发的 MC-Bench 利用 Minecraft 游戏，以用户投票方式对 AI 模型进行创造性和直观能力的评测，旨在弥补传统基准测试的不足，目前 Claude 暂时领先。",
  "summary": "文章介绍了高中生 Adi Singh 开发的 MC-Bench，这是一种新颖的 AI 模型评测方法，更贴合人类对 AI 直观、创造性能力的实际期待。该方法利用 Minecraft 游戏，让 AI 模型根据提示生成 Minecraft 作品，然后由用户投票选出更优的模型。这种评测方式弥补了传统基准测试的不足，传统基准测试过于注重特定任务的性能，而忽略了通用性和创造性。目前，MC-Bench 的榜单上 Claude 暂时领先，但 DeepSeek 等模型也表现出色。文章还提到了其他创意评测方法，如让 AI 模型玩宝可梦游戏，并认为这些新的评测范式可能会推动 AI 的发展。",
